Special Thanks:

Ron Hayter <mystriveal@mac.com> - Provided priceless assistance with figuring
out what actually went on with the .mov files in Mohawk archives, and is
author of Riveal, a program for extracting movies/sounds/etc from Riven.

Tito Dal Canton <tito@indivia.net> - Runs "A Look Inside the Link", and, along
with others, is responsible for reverse engineering the Mohawk archive format
and the resource formats. This is basically ALITL in library form.
   -- http://insidethelink.ortiche.net/

